Class EntityController<E extends Entity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.EntityController<E>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContributorController, ProjectController, StudentController, SubjectController

    public class EntityController<E extends Entity>
extends java.lang.Object
    A class with high-level methods to manipulate a list of entities from a CSV file.
